                  <summary>1 copy of Minhāj al-ʿābidīn by Shaykh Yūsuf Budh Īrichī</summary>
                  <msItem class="http://lccn.loc.gov/sh2006003807 http://lccn.loc.gov/sh85068451" n="1" xml:id="Uk_Delhi_Persian_943D-item1">
                     <textLang mainLang="fa" otherLangs="ar">Persian, Arabic </textLang>
                     <title xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" key="work_21230">Minhāj al-ʿābidīn</title>
                     <title xml:lang="fa" key="work_21230">منهاج العابدين</title>
                     <note>
                        <p>Fine copy, though somewhat damaged, of the Persian translation by <persName key="person_f3907" role="aut">Shaykh Yūsuf Budh Īrichī of Erich</persName> (d. 834/1430-31) for the Arabic original of the same title on Sufism by <persName key="viaf_31996761" role="ant">Imām Abū Ḥāmid Muḥammad ibn Muḥammad al-Ṭūsī al-Ghazālī</persName> (d. 505/1111). 
                        </p>
                        <p>Not dated at end. 
</p>
                        <p>Elegant nastaʿlīq. 
</p>
                        <p>Folios partially unbound; cropped, multiple tide stains, wormholes, later repairs. 
</p>
                        <p>Condition poor. 
</p>
                     </note>
                     <author>
                        <persName xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" key="person_f3907">Shaykh Yūsuf Budh Īrichī</persName>
                        <persName xml:lang="fa" key="person_f3907">شيخ يوسف بده ايرچى</persName>
